    },
    {
      "text": "// Dimensions returns the embedding dimensionality.\nfunc (v *Voyage) Dimensions() int { return v.dims }",
      "contextualizedText": "// internal/embed/voyage.go \u003e method Dimensions\n\n// Dimensions returns the embedding dimensionality.\nfunc (v *Voyage) Dimensions() int { return v.dims }",
